# 🌱 MindMate – Student Mental Health Companion  

MindMate is a **student-first mental well-being app** designed to help learners manage stress, stay positive, and build healthy habits.  
It combines **self-reflection tools, emotional support, and gamified rewards** in one safe, uplifting space.  

## ✨ Features
- 🌈 **Vision Board** – Add images + affirmations to visualize goals  
- 🙏 **Gratitude & Prayer Page** – Calming reflections with animations  
- 🌞 **Daily Affirmations** – Gentle reminders at the click of a button  
- 📝 **Manifestation Journal** – Save affirmations & personal goals  
- 🤝 **Buddy System** – Peer accountability check-ins  
- 💭 **Safe Venting Box** – Private, secure frustration release  
- 📊 **Wellness Tracker** – Sleep, hydration, exercise & screen-time  
- 📞 **Emergency Helplines** – Quick access to counselors & hotlines  
- 🤖 **AI Coping Tips** – Personalized mental health suggestions  
- 🏆 **Gamified Rewards** – Earn badges for consistency & streaks  

## 🛠️ Built With
- [Next.js (App Router)](https://nextjs.org/) – core frontend & routing  
- [React + TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/) – interactive components & type safety  
- [TailwindCSS](https://tailwindcss.com/) – clean, responsive UI  
- [Framer Motion](https://www.framer.com/motion/) – animations for soothing UX  
- [Node.js API Routes](https://nodejs.org/) – journaling & trackers  
- LocalStorage – privacy-first data saving  
- [Vercel](https://vercel.com/) – fast hosting & deployment  

